'''热带风暴阿尔法'''（{{lang-en|Tropical Storm Alpha}}）是[[2005年大西洋飓风季|2005年大西洋飓风季]]第23场获得命名的风暴。由于用来给风暴命名的字母{{lang|en|A}}直至{{lang|en|W}}开头的名称都已用完，阿尔法也成为有纪录以来第1个以希腊字母命名的[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]。10月20日，[[向风群岛|向风群岛]]附近海域形成第二十五号热带低气压，再于同月23日发展成热带风暴，达到最高强度后，气旋有所减弱，再于当天下午登陆[[多米尼加|多米尼加]]。系统穿越[[伊斯帕尼奥拉岛|伊斯帕尼奥拉岛]]后减弱成热带低气压，于10月24日消散，其[[低气压|残留低气压]]被[[飓风威尔玛|飓风威尔玛]]的大规模环流吸收。

阿尔法在伊斯帕尼奥拉岛降下倾盆大雨，贫困的[[海地|海地]]受灾情况尤为严重。降雨引发洪灾和山体滑坡，夺走26条人命，其中海地占17人。多条道路封闭数周之久，数以百计的房屋被毁。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Alpha 2005 track.png}}
10月20日，[[向风群岛|向风群岛]]附近有[[东风波|东风波]]发展<ref name="TCR">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 2006 | title = Tropical Cyclone Report: Tropical Storm Alpha | publisher = NOAA | accessdate = 2013-10-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131029210600/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-AL262005_Alpha.pdf | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-AL262005_Alpha.pdf | format = PDF | archivedate = 2013-10-29 }}</ref>。卫星图像显示，有[[低气压|低气压]]中心同东风波相连，在[[巴巴多斯|巴巴多斯]]附近形成并向[[罗盘方位|西北偏西]]方向移动，其中的[[对流|对流]]活动逐渐增多。由于所在洋面[[风切变|风切变]]很少，对流相应增长，位于[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]的[[多普勒雷达|多普勒气象雷达]]测得数据表明，系统中已有层次分明的[[气旋|气旋状环流]]。<ref name="TCR" />10月22日，低气压区在[[伊斯帕尼奥拉岛|伊斯帕尼奥拉岛]]东南方向海域组织成第二十五号热带低气压<ref name="public1">{{cite web | author = Roberts/Knabb | title = Tropical Depression 25 Public Advisory #1 | date = 2005-10-22 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-08-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140425041357/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2005/pub/al252005.public.001.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2005/pub/al252005.public.001.shtml? | archivedate = 2014-04-25 }}</ref>。此后不久，卫星图像表明系统中已发展出闭合环流，关联的对流也已开始形成带状<ref name="disc1">{{cite web | author = Roberts/Knabb | title = Tropical Depression 25 Discussion #1 | date = 2005-10-22 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-08-16 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2005/dis/al252005.discus.001.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140425021151/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2005/dis/al252005.discus.001.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-04-25 }}</ref>。当天晚上，低气压的组织结构已有显著改善，因此升级成热带风暴并获名“阿尔法”（{{lang|en|Alpha}}），这也是[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]首次以希腊字母为[[北大西洋热带气旋|北大西洋热带气旋]]命名<ref name="public2">{{Cite web | author = Mainelli/Knabb | title = Tropical Storm Alpha Public Advisory #2 | date = 2005-10-22 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-08-16 | archivedate = 2014-04-25 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140425033641/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2005/pub/al252005.public.002.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2005/pub/al252005.public.002.shtml? }}</ref>。

阿尔法进入[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]的[[气象雷达|气象雷达]]覆盖范围，雷达数据显示气旋内已发展出类似[[风眼|风眼墙]]的特征<ref name="disc3">{{cite web | author = Franklin | title = Tropical Storm Alpha Discussion #3 | date = 2005-10-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140425031128/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2005/dis/al252005.discus.003.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-04-25 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-08-16 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2005/dis/al252005.discus.003.shtml? }}</ref>。风暴沿亚热带高压脊的西南边缘移动<ref name="disc3" />，附近有[[飓风威尔玛|飓风威尔玛]]的大规模环流，并受到威尔玛产生的强劲南向气流影响<ref name="disc3" />。阿尔法的环流覆盖面很小，而且正朝伊斯帕尼奥拉岛的山岭地区前进，美国国家飓风中心据此认为，气旋很快就会消散<ref name="disc4">{{cite web | author = Franklin | title = Tropical Storm Alpha Discussion #4 | date = 2005-10-23 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140425041015/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2005/dis/al252005.discus.004.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-04-25 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-08-16 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2005/dis/al252005.discus.004.shtml? }}</ref>。10月23日，风暴达到最高强度，但很快就开始减弱。虽然[[雨带|雨带]]还有对流存在，但下层环流受到陆地的扰乱。阿尔法的层次结构也因此变得混乱，中心模糊不清，难以定位<ref name="disc5">{{cite web | author = Avila | title = Tropical Storm Alpha Discussion #5 | date = 2005-10-23 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-08-16 | archivedate = 2014-04-25 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140425033534/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2005/dis/al252005.discus.005.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2005/dis/al252005.discus.005.shtml? }}</ref>。

10月23日晚，阿尔法[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]伊斯帕尼奥拉岛，风速在陆上行进期间迅速降低<ref name="disc6">{{cite web | author = Avila | title = Tropical Storm Alpha Discussion #6 | date = 2005-10-23 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-08-16 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2005/dis/al252005.discus.006.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140502045114/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2005/dis/al252005.discus.006.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-05-02 }}</ref>。风暴登陆后逐渐减弱，强度降至热带风暴下限，接近热带低气压水平<ref name="disc6" />。气旋弱化的同时，还受到附近飓风威尔玛的强劲南向气流影响，导致难以确认系统中是否还有下层环流<ref name="disc6" />。不过，卫星图像显示伊斯帕尼奥拉岛以北的开放海域上空又发展出新的中心<ref name="disc6" />。次日，阿尔法降级成热带低气压，并重新进入开放水域<ref name="disc7">{{cite web | author = Rhome/Stewart | title = Tropical Depression Alpha Discussion #7 | date = 2005-10-23 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-08-16 | archivedate = 2014-05-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140502055218/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2005/dis/al252005.discus.007.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2005/dis/al252005.discus.007.shtml? }}</ref>。气旋很快发展出拉长的环流中心，表明系统还在继续减弱<ref name="disc8">{{cite web | author = Stewart | title = Tropical Storm Alpha Discussion #8 | date = 2005-10-24 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-08-16 | archivedate = 2014-05-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140502065754/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2005/dis/al252005.discus.008.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2005/dis/al252005.discus.008.shtml? }}</ref>。10月24日，阿尔法的下层中心已完全消亡，只有小规模的[[对流|对流活动]]继续存在。随着系统消散成残留低气压，美国国家飓风中心发布针对气旋的最后一份公布<ref name="disc10">{{cite web | author = Beven | title = Tropical Depression Alpha Discussion #9 | date = 2005-10-24 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-08-17 | archivedate = 2014-05-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140502061238/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2005/dis/al252005.discus.010.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2005/dis/al252005.discus.010.shtml? }}</ref>。残留低气压持续的时间也不长，于10月25日被飓风威尔玛的环流吸收<ref name="TCR" />。

== 防灾措施 ==
10月22日，美国国家飓风中心向伊斯帕尼奥拉岛发布[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴警告]]，并向[[特克斯和凯科斯群岛|特克斯和凯科斯群岛]]和[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]东南部发出热带风暴观察预警，而且预警很快就升级成热带风暴警告<ref name="TCR" />。多米尼加共和国政府下令生活在可能爆发洪灾地区的至少3万居民疏散。10月22至23日，海地政府下令该国可能因热带风暴阿尔法产生降雨的地区进入一级警戒，之后又调整为二级警戒<ref name="relief_haiti_sitrep1">{{cite web | author = Staff Writer | publisher = Relief Web | date = 2005-10-25 | accessdate = 2015-08-16 | title = Haiti: Tropical Storm Alpha, Floods OCHA Situation Report No. 1 | archivedate = 2015-08-16 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150816070115/http://reliefweb.int/report/haiti/haiti-tropical-storm-alpha-floods-ocha-situation-report-no-1 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/haiti/haiti-tropical-storm-alpha-floods-ocha-situation-report-no-1 }}</ref>。海地此前已于10月8至19日间因飓风威尔玛过境遭受洪灾袭击，因此更多降水的威胁尤为严峻<ref name="FloodInfoBulletin">{{cite web | author = International Federation of Red Cross And Red Crescent Societies | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150816070403/http://reliefweb.int/report/haiti/haiti-floods-information-bulletin-no-1 | deadurl = no | publisher = Relief Web | date = 2005-10-31 | accessdate = 2015-08-16 | title = Haiti: Floods Information Bulletin No. 1 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/haiti/haiti-floods-information-bulletin-no-1 | archivedate = 2015-08-16 }}</ref>。该国中央气象局通过已有的各类媒体渠道发布天气公报，明确指示居民做好防范洪灾和泥石流的准备。[[东南省_(海地)|东南省]]地方政府下令首府[[雅克梅勒|雅克梅勒]]予以疏散，国家中央政府调动国家警察、风险管理和灾害常设秘书处，以及公民保护局的人员和资源预先准备紧急行动中心<ref name="relief_haiti_sitrep1" />。

== 影响 ==
从技术上而言，阿尔法的环流是在多米尼加共和国的[[巴拉奥纳|巴拉奥纳]]附近登陆<ref name="TCR" />，但受灾最严重的却是更为穷困的邻国海地<ref name="TCR" /><ref name="relief_haiti_sitrep1" /><ref name="FloodInfoBulletin" />。风暴袭击伊斯帕尼奥拉岛时产生的降雨量为101<ref name="ORE_rain_2005">{{cite web | author = ORE | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120304032951/http://oreworld.org/images/r_mm_eng/2005%20mm_eng.pdf | deadurl = no | publisher = Organization for the Rehabilitation of the Environment | date = 2006-01-01 | accessdate = 2015-08-16 | title = Rainfall - ORE Camp-Perrin, Cayes, Haiti | format = PDF | archivedate = 2012-03-04 | url = http://www.oreworld.org/images/r_mm_eng/2005%20mm_eng.pdf }}</ref>至201毫米之间<ref name="TCR" />，引发多起洪灾和山体滑坡<ref name="relief_haiti_sitrep1" /><ref name="FloodInfoBulletin" />。连接[[太子港|太子港]]和海地[[南部省_(海地)|南部省]]的道路位于[[西部省_(海地)|西部省]][[大戈阿沃|大戈阿沃]]（{{lang|en|Grand-Goave}}）境内路段封闭<ref name="relief_haiti_sitrep1" />。距太子港不远的沿海城市[[莱奥甘|莱奥甘]]有多座桥梁禁止车辆通行，只允许行人使用。马里戈特（{{lang|en|Marigot}}）以东和雅克梅勒以西的多条河流水位上涨，导致道路封闭，[[热雷米|热雷米]]到[[莱凯|莱凯]]之间的主要公路也予封闭<ref name="relief_haiti_sitrep1" /><ref name="FloodInfoBulletin" />。海地其他地区还有多条主要公路因山体滑坡封闭，[[戈纳夫岛|戈纳夫岛]]在经历严酷旱情之后又受到汹涌洪水的摧残，南贝尔有许多排水系统管道被冲毁<ref name="relief_haiti_sitrep1" />。

