海地的灾情主要局限在西部省、东南省和[[大湾省|大湾省]]<ref name="UN_OCHRA_map">{{cite web | author = OCHA | publisher = Relief Web | date = 2005-10-30 | accessdate = 2015-08-16 | title = Haiti: Tropical Storm Alpha and Floods | url = http://reliefweb.int/sites/reliefweb.int/files/resources/B59E7B46A1B3F2D9C12570AA004DECE4-rw_TC_hti301005.pdf | format = PDF | archivedate = 2012-06-14 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120614005654/http://reliefweb.int/sites/reliefweb.int/files/resources/B59E7B46A1B3F2D9C12570AA004DECE4-rw_TC_hti301005.pdf }}</ref>，该国共有17人遇难<ref name="TCR" /><ref name="BBC_rises">{{cite news | author = BBC News | title = Storm Alpha's death toll hits 26 | date = 2005-10-27 | publisher = BBC | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131014091715/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/4381864.stm | accessdate = 2015-08-16 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/4381864.stm | archivedate = 2013-10-14 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。大湾省有两人因河流泛滥溺毙，另两人在洪水期间触电身亡，其中一人是在太子港郊区[[卡勒富尔_(海地)|卡勒富尔]]，另一人则是在南部小镇雅克梅勒<ref name="CBS_8_killed" />；其他死者都是因该国多地的洪灾和山体滑坡导致<ref name="CBS_8_killed">{{cite news | author = CBS news | title = 8 killed by tropical storm Alpha | date = 2005-10-24 | accessdate = 2015-08-16 | url = http://www.cbsnews.com/news/8-killed-by-tropical-storm-alpha/ | work = CBS News | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150816075650/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/8-killed-by-tropical-storm-alpha/ | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-08-16 }}</ref>。整个海地共有243套房屋被毁，另外191套受损<ref name="Relief_French">{{cite web | author = Radio Kiskeya | title = Tropical Storm Alpha | date = 2005-10-25 | publisher = Relief web | accessdate = 2015-08-16 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150816075608/http://reliefweb.int/report/haiti/net-alourdissement-des-pertes-caus%C3%A9es-par-la-temp%C3%AAte-alpha-en-ha%C3%AFti-13-morts-5-disparus | archivedate = 2015-08-16 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/haiti/net-alourdissement-des-pertes-caus%C3%A9es-par-la-temp%C3%AAte-alpha-en-ha%C3%AFti-13-morts-5-disparus }}</ref>。

多明尼加共和国共有9人丧生，其中有两名渔夫于风暴期间在海上失踪，另外7人则是在[[圣斐利-银港|普拉塔港]]等地被河流溢出产生的洪水卷走<ref name="msnbc_8_and_counting">{{cite web | author = AP | publisher = MSNBC | date = 2005-10-24 | accessdate = 2008-08-10 | title = Alpha leaves 8 dead in Haiti before weakening | url = http://www.nbcnews.com/id/9785551/ | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141213040707/http://www.nbcnews.com/id/9785551/ | archivedate = 2014-12-13 }}</ref><ref name="BBC_rises" />。除此以外，多明尼加共和国的受灾情况总体很轻<ref name="TCR" /><ref name="relief_haiti_sitrep1" /><ref name="FloodInfoBulletin" />。

海地政府没有请求[[国际社会|国际社会]]援助，但联合国驻海地稳定特派团、[[联合国开发计划署|联合国开发计划署]]和海地红十字会在风暴来袭前就已在海地展开工作，并且继续在阿尔法过后承担部分救灾工作<ref name="relief_haiti_sitrep1" />。面对洪灾，红十字会雅克梅勒地区分部额外发放了400份净水药片，11箱[[高能量饼干|高能量饼干]]和10箱净身皂<ref name="FloodInfoBulletin" />。

== 命名和纪录 ==
飓风威尔玛之后，[[2005年大西洋飓风季|2005年大西洋飓风季]]的全部21个预先确定的风暴名称都已用完，接下来如果还有热带气旋达到热带风暴标准，则会以希腊字母命名，其中第1个就是“[[Α|阿尔法]]”。1972年时，曾有过一场[[亚热带气旋|亚热带风暴]]以阿尔法[[1972年亚热带风暴阿尔法|命名]]，但2005年则是首次有热带天气系统以阿尔法命名。<ref name="newscientist">{{cite web | author = Jeff Hecht | publisher = NewScientist.com news service | date = 2005-10-24 | accessdate = 2008-08-10 | title = Wilma hits Florida, Alpha breaks record | archivedate = 2008-04-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080409224212/http://www.newscientist.com/article.ns?id=dn8198 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.newscientist.com/article.ns?id=dn8198 }}</ref>

气象机构原以为阿尔法是本季第22场获得命名的风暴，打破[[1933年大西洋飓风季|1933年大西洋飓风季]]保持的21场纪录。但飓风季过后的重新分析结果表明，10月4日还曾有过1场[[2005年亚速尔亚热带风暴|此前未发现的亚热带风暴]]<ref name="AzoresTCR">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | date = 2006-04-10 | title = Tropical Cyclone Report: Unnamed Subtropical Storm | publisher = NOAA | accessdate = 2013-11-07 | format = PDF | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131107164849/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-AL212005_Unnamed.pdf | archivedate = 2013-11-07 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-AL212005_Unnamed.pdf }}</ref>，这样阿尔法就成为本季第23场风暴。此外，阿尔法还是第一场在风暴名称用完后以希腊字母命名的热带风暴。<ref name="TCR" />

